Nu plec.

265
00:30:34.300 --> 00:30:35.728
Ascunde aia.

266
00:30:38.766 --> 00:30:39.766
Ai înțeles?

267
00:30:40.700 --> 00:30:43.332
Revino-ți odată!

268
00:30:43.333 --> 00:30:44.466
Hai!

269
